original_query: SELECT u.Id, c.UserId FROM comments as c, votes as v, users as u WHERE u.Id = c.UserId AND u.Id = v.UserId AND c.CreationDate>=CAST('2010-10-01 20:45:26' AS TIMESTAMP) AND c.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-05 12:51:17' AS TIMESTAMP) AND v.BountyAmount<=50 AND u.UpVotes=0 AND u.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-12 03:25:34' AS TIMESTAMP)
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT comments.userid AS E1_userid FROM comments AS comments WHERE comments.creationdate >= TIMESTAMP '2010-10-01 20:45:26' AND comments.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-05 12:51:17'
CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT users.id AS E3_id FROM users AS users WHERE users.upvotes = 0 AND users.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-12 03:25:34'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E1.E1_userid=E3.E3_id)
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT votes.userid AS E2_userid FROM votes AS votes WHERE votes.bountyamount <= 50
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E1_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E1_stage1_0.E1_userid=E2.E2_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1_stage1_1 WHERE E1_stage1_1.E1_userid=E3.E3_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1_stage1_1 WHERE E1_stage1_1.E1_userid=E2.E2_userid)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E1_stage1_1.E1_userid AS E1_userid, E3_stage2_0.E3_id AS E3_id FROM E1_stage1_1, E3_stage2_0, E2_stage2_0 WHERE E1_stage1_1.E1_userid=E3_stage2_0.E3_id AND E1_stage1_1.E1_userid=E2_stage2_0.E2_userid
